org.hibernate.query.spi

Class DoubleStreamDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.query.spi.DoubleStreamDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable, BaseStream<Double,DoubleStream>, DoubleStream

    public class DoubleStreamDecorator
extends Object
implements DoubleStream
    The DoubleStreamDecorator wraps a Java DoubleStream and registers a closeHandler which is passed further to any resulting Stream.

    The goal of the DoubleStreamDecorator is to close the underlying DoubleStream upon calling a terminal operation.

    Since:
    5.4
